author: COMSOL
description: This example simulates the heat profile in an air-cooled cylindrical battery in 3D. The battery is placed in a matrix in a battery pack. The thermal model is coupled to a 1D-battery model that is used to generate a heat source in the active battery material.
label: li_battery_thermal_3d.mph
